    "title": "MRR (Monthly Recurring Revenue)",
    "category": "revenue",
    "content": "MRR - ключевая метрика для SaaS. Расчет: Сумма всех recurring подписок за месяц. Компоненты: New MRR (новые клиенты) + Expansion MRR (upsell/cross-sell) + Reactivation MRR - Contraction MRR (downgrade) - Churn MRR. Growth rate benchmark: 10-20% MoM для early stage, 5-7% для mature. Net Revenue Retention > 100% - признак здорового SaaS.",
    "tags": ["revenue", "mrr", "growth"],
    "metadata": {
      "formulas": {
        "mrr_growth_rate": "((MRR_end - MRR_start) / MRR_start) × 100",
        "net_revenue_retention": "((MRR_start + Expansion - Contraction - Churn) / MRR_start) × 100"
      },
      "benchmarks": {
        "early_stage_growth": "10-20% MoM",
